```plantuml
@startuml jkahn117_aws-news

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AWS CloudFront" as CloudFront
participant "AWS AppSync" as AppSync
participant "AWS Lambda (Content Serving)" as ContentLambda
participant "Amazon ElastiCache (Redis)" as ElastiCache
participant "Amazon S3" as S3
participant "Amazon DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "Amazon EventBridge" as EventBridge
participant "AWS Lambda (Image Processing)" as ImageLambda
participant "Kinesis Data Firehose" as KinesisFirehose
participant "Amazon Pinpoint" as Pinpoint

User -> Frontend: Access Website
Frontend -> CloudFront: Request Content
CloudFront -> AppSync: Query Articles
AppSync -> ElastiCache: Check Cache
alt Cache Hit
    ElastiCache -> AppSync: Return Cached Articles
else Cache Miss
    AppSync -> ContentLambda: Fetch Articles
    ContentLambda -> DynamoDB: Query Metadata
    ContentLambda -> S3: Retrieve Article Content
    ContentLambda -> ElastiCache: Update Cache
    ContentLambda -> AppSync: Return Articles
end
AppSync -> CloudFront: Deliver Content
CloudFront -> Frontend: Serve Content
Frontend -> Pinpoint: Send User Interaction Data
Pinpoint -> KinesisFirehose: Stream Data
Frontend -> EventBridge: Trigger `article_created` Event
EventBridge -> ImageLambda: Process Images
ImageLambda -> S3: Store Processed Images
ImageLambda -> DynamoDB: Update Image Metadata

@enduml
```